% MP:

% Whenever you have manually modified the print style for a theory constant
% it could be a good a idea to add its definition to this file.
%
% The definitions here will overdefine/overwrite the standard print style 
% generated by post2tex.

% Numbers (amsfonts!)
\def\Nat{\mathbb N}

\def\Rat{\mathbb Q}

% Types
